                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Runyon</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-10-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 28, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Telegram received this morning. I have seen minister for foreign affairs and made
                    urgent representations according to instructions. Immediate action or reply not
                    probable on account of present Government conditions.</p>
            </div>
